By choosing prayer bonus over ranged accuracy, you will need to pick up and drink 23-42 fewer prayer potions. If you are able to pick up prayer potions and continue throwing chinchompas ''without losing any ticks or unstacking the monkeys too much'', which is very unrealistic, with max ranged bonus gear you would gain no more than an extra 5,000 experience per hour. It is much more likely that players will waste more time picking up more prayer potions per hour than the minimal extra damage output saves, resulting in lower experience per hour. For this reason prayer bonus gear is considered superior to having higher ranged accuracy, and it also makes training less intense.

Choosing prayer bonus over ranged accuracy is also better if you are bringing a [[bonecrusher necklace]] switch to restore prayer points, as you would spend less time not wearing a necklace of anguish. With divine ranging potions however, at certain levels and/or with certain setups you will not gain a max hit from wearing the necklace of anguish. In that case, wearing the bonecrusher necklace with high ranged accuracy equipment ([[pegasian boots]], [[archers ring (i)]]) becomes slightly better, as your prayer will remain almost full the entire time due to the effects of the bonecrusher necklace. With 2 dancing accounts, this method also allows you to fully AFK without the need to drink or pick up any prayer potions.

